location.fullValue: Odyssey Plan, Bennett Village : The Explorer Collection

data.description: Hurry to see this amazingly spacious, true open concept ranch style home in the Centennial neighborhood of Bennett, Colorado. This spectacular home is perfectly located on an over-sized lot, with a classic brick and siding exterior, and a rare over-sized 2 car garage. The inviting entry awaits with extended laminate floors, high ceilings and flooded with natural light through the large windows. The main living area offers an abundance of space with a large remodeled kitchen that features upgraded bright white cabinets, extended counters, convenient center island, and all appliances are included. The dining area is the ideal space for everyday meals or large family gatherings. Relax in the perfectly situated family room that will accommodate today's largest televisions and furnishings as you cozy up to the brick faced wood burning fireplace. The main floor is complete with 4 bedrooms, and a nicely updated full bathroom. The basement has been professionally finished to add a huge recreation area that is perfect for a game room, theater or workout area. There is NEW CARPET,  a convenient bathroom / laundry area, and plenty of unfinished storage space. You will love the size of the outdoor living area that features a large cement patio, fully fenced yard, and bring your green thumb and plan to turn this area into an entertainers dream. Other features include an attached two car garage, upgraded windows, new paint and siding, newer roof, NO HOA's,  and so much more. Bennett is a growing town near the eastern end of Colfax Avenue, 30 minutes from Aurora. It has a small downtown area with restaurants and local businesses to browse.  Located at 5,485 feet above sea level on the great plains, the community is continuously expanding into a hub for services along I-70. This one won't last....see it today!!!
